<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2">
<h2 id="Family">Family</h2>
<span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Bruce_Bueno_de_Mesquita&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Family"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span>
</div>
<p>Bueno de Mesquita has three children and six grandchildren. His son, Ethan Bueno de Mesquita, is a political scientist currently serving as dean of the <a href="/wiki/Harris_School_of_Public_Policy" title="Harris School of Public Policy">Harris School of Public Policy</a> at the <a href="/wiki/University_of_Chicago" title="University of Chicago">University of Chicago</a>.
</p>
